## ✨ What is LearnFlow?

LearnFlow is a **YouTube-powered Learning Management System** that lets anyone turn a YouTube playlist or video into a fully structured bootcamp course — complete with modules, lessons, progress tracking, and a clean video player.

No more jumping between browser tabs. Just paste a link and start learning.

