## 🖼️ App Flow

```
 Login Screen
      │
      ▼
 Dashboard
  ├── Paste YouTube URL
  ├── Click "Create Bootcamp"
  └── See Bootcamp Cards
      │
      ▼
 Course Page
  ├── Sidebar (Modules + Lessons)
  ├── YouTube Video Player
  ├── Progress Bar
  └── Mark Complete Button
```

