## ⚙️ Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- Node.js v18+
- npm v9+

### Installation

```bash
# 1. Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/akhil3145/LMS_2.o.git

# 2. Go into the project folder
cd LMS_2.o

# 3. Install dependencies
npm install

# 4. Start the dev server
npm run dev

# On Windows PowerShell if blocked:
npm.cmd run dev
```

Open **http://localhost:5173** in your browser.

